## Get a specific Question

<%= partial "includes/requests/get", locals: { url: "https://api.tito.io/v2/an-account/awesome-conf/questions/1000001" } %>

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

<%= partial 'includes/questions/show.json' %>

This endpoint retrieves a specific `Question`.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://api.tito.io/v2/:account/:event/questions/:question`

## Creating a new Question

<%= partial "includes/requests/post", locals: {
      url: "https://api.tito.io/v2/an-account/awesome-conf/questions",
      parameters: {
        data: {
          type: "questions",
          attributes: {
            field_type: 'Checkboxes',
            options: "Small\nMedium\nLarge\nExtra Large",
            title: 'T-Shirt Size'
          }
        }
      }
    } %>

This endpoint creates a `Question` on the given `Event`.

### HTTP Request

`POST https://api.tito.io/v2/:account/:event/questions`

### Parameters

Parameter | Type | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
<%- data.questions.attributes.reject { |name, attributes| name == 'slug' }.each do |name, attributes| -%>
<%= name %> | `<%= attributes["type"] %>` | <%= attributes["description"] %>
<%- end -%>

